listitem.para:
   service.nylon is now declared using named instances. As
   an example:

services.nylon = {
  enable = true;
  acceptInterface = "br0";
  bindInterface = "tun1";
  port = 5912;
};

   should be replaced with:

services.nylon.myvpn = {
  enable = true;
  acceptInterface = "br0";
  bindInterface = "tun1";
  port = 5912;
};

   this enables you to declare a SOCKS proxy for each uplink.

overridePackages function no longer exists. It is replaced by
overlays. For example, the following code:
let pkgs = import <nixpkgs> {}; in pkgs.overridePackages (self: super: ...)
should be replaced by:
let pkgs = import <nixpkgs> {}; in import pkgs.path { overlays = [(self: super: ...)]; }
